---
title: Spicy Bacon-Pepperoni Pizza with Hot Honey Drizzle and Garlic-Butter Crust
description: Calling all pizza lovers! Piles of bacon and pepperoni combine with a blistered crust brushed with garlic butter in this 'za. A drizzle of hot honey elevates the flavours to new heights for an unforgettable DIY pizza night!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spicy-bacon-pepperoni-pizza-43531dcb.jpg
